(129, 'adidas Laceless X Speedflow.3 FG &#8211; Meteorite', 'BRN001', 'KTG005', 19, 99.99, 'asset/product/129.jpg', ' Meteorite Laceless X Speedflow.3 Firm Ground Cleats  Save the planet and up your game with the Laceless X Speedflow.3 FG.   This generation of adidas speed cleats offers a 20% semitransluscent upper that has been made with a minimum of 50% recycled content allowing you to be comfortable and quick. A laceless upper construction also allows you to stay one step ahead. Where else can you gain speed and save the planet all at an affordable price?  Interested in some of our other cleats from  adidas? Check \'em out today!  ', 1),
