(243, 'Puma King Platinum 21 FG &#8211; Black &#038; Neon Citrus', 'BRN003', 'KTG005', 42, 199.99, 'asset/product/243.jpg', ' The cleat built for royalty is back! The redesigned Puma King is more modern than ever but is still home to some classic features. A newly modernized upper that still features classic K-Leather will keep any leather fans at ease. Also built with a knit tongue in the upper you will for sure stay locked in. If you\'re still looking for a reason to get your hands on the King, these cleats have been the go to for legends like Maradona and Pele! Why not play like a legend today? If you want to explore all your options check out the Puma Ultra  and the Future today! ', 1),
